{
  "stem": "33.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 128,
      "text": "We were not allowed to step back in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 129,
      "text": "But there were mothers who had a daughter there, maybe, for a couple of days, just to give her a little rest in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 130,
      "text": "There were daughters who might have mothered their sisters' sisters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 131,
      "text": "And they all were watching taking their loved ones, of course, in the trucks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 132,
      "text": "One of the girls, a 20-year-old, very beautiful girl had her mother-- happened to have mother there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 133,
      "text": "And she risked her life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 134,
      "text": "She went back, and she asked Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 135,
      "text": "Mengele to save her mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 136,
      "text": "He looked at her, and he asked, how old is your mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 137,
      "text": "She said, my mother is 40 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 138,
      "text": "He looked at her again, and said, your mother lived enough, and sent her off to her death.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 139,
      "text": "I mean, he was a real monster.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 140,
      "text": "He took sheer delight in murdering as many people as he possibly could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 141,
      "text": "He didn't just follow orders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 142,
      "text": "It was his goal in life, and it was his big passion in life, I think, to murder Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 143,
      "text": "After we witnessed all these, and we were told to just turn around, and go, we all had the feeling that we might go to the same destination.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 144,
      "text": "But, again, we didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 145,
      "text": "We went to the other side of the tracks, where the so-called working camps were because they were taking people-- IG Farben Industry had a plant near Auschwitz, and some people were taken to work details from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 146,
      "text": "We were taken there, and eventually, after about three weeks, we were taken away-- we were supposed to go into small working camps to work as nurses or some doctors in these little clinics where they had maybe first aid kits or dispense an aspirin.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 147,
      "text": "Really not more than that.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
